Nigerian prophet TB Joshua shocked South Africans on Saturday morning when he declared on a service that was aired live on his television channel that Nkandla will be swept away by floods next month.&#8220;While in the spirit, I traveled to South Africa. I saw it was the month of February. I saw a huge disaster in the province of KZN, Nkandla to be specific. It will rain for a week and there will be floods. The president&#8217;s house will be swept away by the floods. This cannot be prevented, but pray for Mr. Presdient Zuma.&#8221; said Prophet Joshua.President Zuma has not publicly said anything about the prophecy as yet, but sources revealed that he is very scared. Pray for him South Africa.